《最终幻想》获得了媒体的好评和商业成功；最初的FC版在日本的出貨量達52万份<ref name="520K"/>。截至2003年3月31日，游戏全版本的全球出货量達199万份，其中日本121万份，日本以外78万份<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.jp.square-enix.com/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200402090000-01.pdf#page=27 |title=Titles of game software with worldwide shipments exceeding 1 million copies |accessdate=2018-12-13 |publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] |page=27 |archive-date=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109063558/http://www.jp.square-enix.com/ir/e/explanatory/download/0404-200402090000-01.pdf#page=27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而之後上市的PSP版，截至2007年11月19日出货量達14万份<ref>{{cite web | title=FY2007 First-Half Period Results Briefing Session | date=2007-11-19 | url=http://www.jp.square-enix.com/ir/e/explanatory/download/20071119en_20.pdf | publisher=[[Square_Enix|Square Enix]] | accessdate=2018-12-13 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304051455/http://www.jp.square-enix.com/ir/e/explanatory/download/20071119en_20.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2006年3月日本《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》举办的读者票选百大游戏名单中，《最终幻想》排名第63位<ref>{{cite web | author=Edge Staff | title=Japan Votes on All Time Top 100 | work=[[Edge_(magazine)|Edge]] | date=2006-03-03 | url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100/ | accessdate=2008-10-16 | archive-date=2008-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723051728/http://www.edge-online.com/features/japan-votes-all-time-top-100 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]]用户在2005制作了一份类似名单，《最终幻想》排名第76位<ref>{{cite web|title=Fall 2005: 10-Year Anniversary Contest - The 10 Best Games Ever |url=http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 |publisher=[[GameFAQs|GameFAQs]] |accessdate=2008-10-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090316073741/http://www.gamefaqs.com/features/contest/top10 |archivedate=2009-03-16 }}</ref>。游戏在《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》举办的全任天堂主机200佳游戏中，游戏排名第49位<ref name="NP200">{{cite journal |journal=[[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |first=Pete |last=Michaud | title=NP Top 200 |volume=199 |pages=42–43|date=January 2006}}</ref>。在2008年8月，《任天堂力量》将游戏列为第19佳FC游戏，称赞其和《[[勇者斗恶龙_(游戏)|勇者斗恶龙]]》创立了游戏机角色扮演游戏的基础，并以其史诗般剧情、升级、随机战和角色职业为例援引<ref>{{cite journal |date=August 2008 |title=Nintendo Power - The 20th Anniversary Issue! |volume=231 |series= [[Nintendo_Power|Nintendo Power]] |issue=231 |page=71 |pages= |publisher=[[Future_US|Future US]] |location=[[San_Francisco|San Francisco]] |format=Magazine }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]编辑将《最终幻想》列为第11佳游戏机游戏，称游戏职业系统变化多样，并称赞其以交通工具穿行世界的手段<ref>{{cite web | title=11. Final Fantasy – Top 100 NES Games | url=http://uk.ign.com/top-100-nes-games/11.html | publisher=IGN | accessdate=2010-03-22 | archive-date=2009-10-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091023104724/http://uk.ign.com/top-100-nes-games/11.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《最终幻想》是最具影响力的早期游戏机角色扮演游戏之一，并在此类游戏创立与普及中扮演重要角色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/games/final-fantasy/nes-6010|title=Final Fantasy (Final Fantasy I)|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2008-12-22|archive-date=2015-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151220163752/http://www.ign.com/games/final-fantasy/nes-6010|dead-url=no}}</ref>。IGN的馬特·卡薩馬西納（{{lang|en|Matt Casamassina}}称，《最终幻想》的情节比初代《勇者斗恶龙》更深更迷人<ref>{{cite web | first=Matt | last=Casamassina | title=State of the RPG: GameCube | publisher=IGN | date=2005-07-19 | url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2005/07/19/state-of-the-rpg-gamecube | accessdate=2008-10-16 | archive-date=2011-08-05 | archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/60hQ1V0x2?url=http://cube.ign.com/articles/634/634965p1.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。现代评论通常称游戏以当今眼光看来节奏不佳，游戏太多时间用来故意打随机战获得经验和金钱，而非探索与解谜。其他评论认为等级建设与一些探索是游戏最有趣的部分<ref name="Origins">{{cite web| last=Dunham| first=Jeremy| title=Final Fantasy Origins Review| publisher=IGN| date=2003-04-15| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/04/15/final-fantasy-origins| accessdate=2008-10-16| archive-date=2013-02-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130212050417/http://www.ign.com/articles/2003/04/15/final-fantasy-origins| dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Fami通》最早在1987年称初代《最终幻想》是众多《勇者斗恶龙》模式模仿品之一<ref>{{cite web|last=Fujii |first=Daiji |authorlink= |coauthors= |date= |year=2003 |month= |url=http://www.e.okayama-u.ac.jp/~dfujii/Option.pdf |title=Entrepreneurial Choices of Strategic Options in Japan's RPG Development |format=PDF |work= |page=14 |publisher= |accessdate=2006-08-12 |curly= |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081230090342/http://www.e.okayama-u.ac.jp/~dfujii/Option.pdf |archivedate=2008-12-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。游戏被认为是系列中最微弱且最难的一作<ref name="WSC" />。

后来的《最终幻想》版本多获媒体喜爱。IGN的皮尔·施耐德（{{lang|en|Peer Schneider}}）喜欢WonderSwan Color版本，并称赞其改进的画面，其中特别是环境、角色与怪兽图像<ref name="WSC">{{cite web| last=Schneider| first=Peer| date=2001-02-12| title=Final Fantasy (Import)| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/02/13/final-fantasy-import| publisher=IGN| accessdate=2008-10-16| archive-date=2013-06-25| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625200137/http://www.ign.com/articles/2001/02/13/final-fantasy-import| dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Fami通》给该版本打了30/40分<ref name="fam_wonderswan">''ワンダースワン - ファイナルファンタジー''. Weekly Famitsu. No.915 Pt.2. Pg.112. 30 June 2006.</ref>。《最终幻想I·II高级套装》通常获得好评；《[[GamePro|GamePro]]》称音乐“奇幻”，图像“恰到好处的优雅复古”<ref>{{cite web|last=Fox |first=Fennec |title=Final Fantasy Origins |work=[[GamePro|GamePro]] |date=2003-04-07 |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/28844/final-fantasy-origins/ |accessdate=2008-10-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080918074637/http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/28844/final-fantasy-origins/ |archivedate=2008-09-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。对《最终幻想I·II Advance》通常获得正面评价，IGN的杰里米·邓纳姆（{{lang|en|Jeremy Dunham}}）特别称赞了改进的英文翻译，称其胜于之前任何游戏版本<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/11/30/final-fantasy-i-ii-dawn-of-souls|title=Final Fantasy I & II: Dawn of Souls|publisher=IGN|first=Jeremy|last=Dunham|date=2004-11-30|accessdate=2008-12-22|archive-date=2012-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120917024836/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/11/30/final-fantasy-i-ii-dawn-of-souls|dead-url=no}}</ref>。PlayStation Portable版本在评论上并未像之前版本那样成功；[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]的Kevin VanOrd引以了大幅改进的视觉效果，但称新增的随机战敌人和改进的画面并无太多附加价值<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/final-fantasy-anniversary-edition/reviews/final-fantasy-anniversary-edition-review-6173084/?tag=tabs%3Breviews|title=Final Fantasy Anniversary Edition Review|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|first=Kevin|last=VanOrd|date=2007-06-25|accessdate=2008-12-22|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921060909/http://www.gamespot.com/final-fantasy-anniversary-edition/reviews/final-fantasy-anniversary-edition-review-6173084/?tag=tabs%3Breviews|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《Advance》包排在《任天堂力量》200佳游戏名单的第76位<ref name="NP200" />。

== 影响 ==
游戏原声专辑也和《[[最终幻想II|最终幻想II]]》的配乐于1989年一同发行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rpgfan.com/soundtracks/ff1&2/index.html|title=All Sounds of Final Fantasy I - II|publisher=RPGFan|author=Schweitzer, Ben; Gann, Patrick|accessdate=2008-07-09|archive-date=2013-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116215146/http://rpgfan.com/soundtracks/ff1%262/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些游戏曲目成为最终幻想系列的基本要素，包括标题界面用[[琶音|琶音]]演奏的《Prelude》；在游戏开头过桥时播放的背景音乐，后来成为最终幻想主题曲的《Opening Theme》；以及队伍每场战斗胜利后播放的《Victory Fanfare》。战斗前奏乐也在系列中利用了多次<ref name="FFI" />。在角色首次通过科利尼亚桥时播放的的主题音乐成为了系列主题曲，并在处《最终幻想XIII》外的大多数最终幻想游戏中出现。《最终幻想》还改编为电子游戏主题卡通连续剧《[[N队长：游戏高手|N队长：游戏高手]]》（{{lang|en|''Captain N: The Game Master''}}）的最后一集《{{lang|en|The Fractured Fantasy of Captain N}}》<ref>{{cite web| title=Final Fantasy Retrospective - Part X| publisher=[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]| date=2007-09-25| url=http://www.gametrailers.com/full-episodes/y25ol1/gt-retrospectives-part-x| accessdate=2008-10-16| archive-date=2012-10-09| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121009055116/http://www.gametrailers.com/full-episodes/y25ol1/gt-retrospectives-part-x| dead-url=no}}</ref>。由[[布莱恩·克莱文杰|布莱恩·克莱文杰]]（{{lang|en|Brian Clevinger}}）创作，以[[精灵_(计算机图形)|子图形]]为基础的[[网络漫画|网络漫画]][[8位剧场|8位剧场]]模仿了游戏，并从2001年3月开始在游戏社群非常流行<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=2&cId=3145208|title=Will Strip For Games: Gaming Comics Online|publisher=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]|first=Nich|last=Maragos|date=2005-11-07|accessdate=2008-12-23|archive-date=2007-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927194442/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?pager.offset=2&cId=3145208|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

游戏在[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]衍生出两个直系跨界前传：《[[最终幻想_纷争|最终幻想 纷争]]》和《[[最终幻想_纷争012|最终幻想 纷争012]]》。改编自天野喜孝所设计主角的光之战士和加兰多分别为《最终幻想》的英雄和反派。光之战士日版由[[关俊彦|关俊彦]]配音，加兰多由[[内海贤二|内海贤二]]配音，美版两人均由[[克里斯托弗·沙巴特|克里斯托弗·沙巴特]]（{{lang|en|Christopher Sabat}}）配音<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/dissidia-final-fantasy/previews/dissidia-final-fantasy-hands-on-6195546/|title=Dissidia: Final Fantasy Hands-On|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|first=Hirohiko|last=Niizumi|date=2008-08-06|accessdate=2008-12-23|archive-date=2012-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120203121755/http://www.gamespot.com/dissidia-final-fantasy/previews/dissidia-final-fantasy-hands-on-6195546/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。两个游戏都将《最终幻想》的背景信息加入了游戏。举例而言，《最终幻想 纷争012》中将《最终幻想》的世界命名为“世界A”，以此区别《纷争》的世界B<ref>{{cite video game|title=Dissidia 012 Final Fantasy |developer=Square Enix |publisher=Square Enix |date=2011-03-22|platform=PlayStation Portable |quote='''Report 7:''' World: A / Place: Town on the Hawk's Wing / Forgotten Memories -07- "So what you just told is all memory you have inherited?" / Yes. Memory succession is a dying art. In order to preserve this memory for a longer time, I thought it best to leave it in writing. / "Do you think there is any relation between your memory and the Five Fiends wreaking havoc on our world now?" / That, I cannot say with any certainty. But there are curious similarities as to where things happened. / Where the rip in time-space occurred, and where the Four Fiends now dwell... The scenery in both locations match with what remain in my memory. / "Thank you for sharing your story. It shall be passed on as recorded." / Lukahn, please let me ask you one question before we finish. The Warrior of Light, the one you predicted would save the world from this calamity with crystal in hand, is he really coming? / "I am called an oracle, but I am actually a historian." / "History must always converge. I feel faint signs of it coming from the distant worlds. / The Warrior of Light shall come indeed. / And he shall liberate this world... no, the people of this world from the cycle of positivity."}}</ref>。

